snippet.title: Defend The Night - Alpha 1 Trailer
snippet.description:
Alpha 1 game teaser for our upcoming dark fantasy MMORPG, Defend The Night!  Register now at https://www.defendthenightgame.com/register/

Check out our revamped website with newly released info on Lore, Races, Classes, World Map, and much more: https://www.defendthenightgame.com

Defend The Night is being developed by Ninja Loot Games: http://www.ninjalootgames.com
